10) Parallel Stream

✅ What is Parallel Stream?
Parallel stream runs stream operations using multiple threads.

How to use?
list.parallelStream()

Example
import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        List<Integer> nums = Arrays.asList(1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8);

        nums.parallelStream()
            .forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}
📌 Important:
❌ order may change
✅ faster for big data

